title: Recipe Analysis Tool
description: Collaborated to build a website that analyzes correlations between nutritional content and recipe popularity using Python, pandas, and Plotly. Contributed to designing the backend for data cleaning, merging large datasets, and generating statistical insights and visualizations.

title: Robot Evolutionary Simulation
description: Recreated a 1968 Harvard University experiment to study evolutionary effects on robot populations. Robots inherited random behaviors, which evolved into successful strategies through selective reproduction with the top 50% of the population.

title: Dynamic To-Do List
description: Developed a dynamic To-Do list application that allows users to add, delete, and display tasks efficiently. Implemented features such as dynamic memory allocation, system data integration, and input validation.
